{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:1",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
      "translation": "衝撃[1]、",
      "footnotes": "[1]　この「衝撃」とは、その恐怖と戦慄（せんりつ）によって創造物に衝撃を与える、復活の日*のこと（アル＝クルトゥビー2０：1６４参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:2",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
      "translation": "衝撃とは何か？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:3",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
      "translation": "衝撃とは何かを、何があなたに知らせるか？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:4",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ",
      "translation": "（衝撃とは、）人々が散り散りになった蛾のようになり、[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　その数の多さ、哀（あわ）れさと、散らばり、混乱した様子が蛾に譬（たと）えられている（アル＝バイダーウィー５：５22参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:5",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ",
      "translation": "また山々が、梳かれた羊毛のようになる日。[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　復活の日*の山々の変化については、洞窟章４７の訳注を参照。"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:6",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
      "translation": "自分の（善行の）秤が（悪行の秤より）重かった者はといえば、[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　復活の日*の秤については、高壁章８の訳注も参照。"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:7",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ",
      "translation": "彼は（天国で）満足な生活の中にある。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:8",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
      "translation": "また、自分の（善行の）秤が（悪行の秤より）軽かった者はといえば、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:9",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ",
      "translation": "その落ち着く先は、墜落。[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「落ち着く先（ウンム）」には、「頭」という解釈もある。その場合、「頭から業火へと墜落する」という意味となる。また、「墜落」とは、底知れず墜落する場所である、地獄の別称（アル＝バガウィー５：2９７参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:10",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ",
      "translation": "それが何かを、何があなたに知らせるか？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 600,
      "verse_key": "101:11",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ",
      "translation": "（それは）酷熱の業火である。",
      "footnotes": ""
    }
  ]
}